{"id": "ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 393, "displayName": {"text": "Sasa Japanese Restaurant", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Multi-course Japanese-American kaiseki & a la carte options offered in warm, modern quarters.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FNWJIUnFPRjl0TlhWSU5sY3hlbVZLVTBoalRsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The food was amazing! The restaurant had a lovely ambiance with a sushi bar.\n\nWe ordered the creamy scallops roll, salmon gozen bento set, and salmon taster nigiri set.\nEverything was delicious! Highly recommend this place, we’ll definitely be back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The food was amazing! The restaurant had a lovely ambiance with a sushi bar.\n\nWe ordered the creamy scallops roll, salmon gozen bento set, and salmon taster nigiri set.\nEverything was delicious! Highly recommend this place, we’ll definitely be back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amy B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115118820285274881960/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOoldS4HxXpjRAlpFSBPXgZKsTGNTglv9FvkGeGl9qxLnwrg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T02:14:08.990668882Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FNWJIUnFPRjl0TlhWSU5sY3hlbVZLVTBoalRsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FNWJIUnFPRjl0TlhWSU5sY3hlbVZLVTBoalRsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80858145f40b31e1:0x283a08661e21a5ce"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kNGFsZFdObGRaTlhGM2RYRjFSVGxHWjI1dkxWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here on Tuesday night for dinner. Kinda busy, we ordered toro don, sushi moriawase, creamy salmon roll and some à la carte as well. All I can say is the FISH are all fresh. Servers are very friendly and they will check on you make sure everything is ok even though it was busy at the restaurant. Definitely will come back soon.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here on Tuesday night for dinner. Kinda busy, we ordered toro don, sushi moriawase, creamy salmon roll and some à la carte as well. All I can say is the FISH are all fresh. Servers are very friendly and they will check on you make sure everything is ok even though it was busy at the restaurant. Definitely will come back soon.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Vicky", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106825290298271555018/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1BFC8JJtZfMP0u7gGan-xW2VGWHFQTX2tlMu4Hv0vUwqA4oh4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-29T07:08:20.562271352Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kNGFsZFdObGRaTlhGM2RYRjFSVGxHWjI1dkxWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kNGFsZFdObGRaTlhGM2RYRjFSVGxHWjI1dkxWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80858145f40b31e1:0x283a08661e21a5ce"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKdFQySkphRUppVTA5SFRuQTRhR3N0V2poRlFuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The omakase was a great experience! Lots of great food with some unique flavors. Highly recommend if you want to try a variety of sushi.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The omakase was a great experience! Lots of great food with some unique flavors. Highly recommend if you want to try a variety of sushi.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Zachary Ruiz", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102329218197497003316/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaRGQsCkBMcobrK0EP7GypsTFmTD2YfyF6lGHnxpaDOGB0HQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-19T02:02:43.934188470Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKdFQySkphRUppVTA5SFRuQTRhR3N0V2poRlFuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKdFQySkphRUppVTA5SFRuQTRhR3N0V2poRlFuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858145f40b31e1:0x283a08661e21a5ce"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oR2FFVjFVWFo0ZWxGaGRIbFBiWHB3VURaMloyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Birthday lunch! Friend surprised me with lunch here. Omakase beautifully presented and you can really tell the chefs care about the quality of the fish. Each piece of nigiri felt thoughtfully prepared. All of it was perfectly seasoned and the fish was incredibly fresh.\n\nSome standout bites for me were the uni and ikura spoon, Wagyu, and the lightly torched salmon nigiri. The flavors were clean, balanced, and melt-in-your-mouth good. We also had the yuzu tea and sakura drink which paired really nicely with the meal. The omakase pacing was good! Just enough time to enjoy each piece without feeling rushed.\n\nThe restaurant itself has a cozy, intimate sushi bar vibe and the service was attentive throughout the meal. It's a great spot in Japantown for a date night or special occasion if you're craving high-quality sushi in the city.\n\nTotal for two came out to about $370 with two omakases ($98 each), supplements ($35 each), drinks ($6.50 per tea), tax, and tip. Worth it to add the $35 supplement of the O-Toro w/ caviar, uni ikura spoon, A5 wagyu. worth it for the experience. Would happily come back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Birthday lunch! Friend surprised me with lunch here. Omakase beautifully presented and you can really tell the chefs care about the quality of the fish. Each piece of nigiri felt thoughtfully prepared. All of it was perfectly seasoned and the fish was incredibly fresh.\n\nSome standout bites for me were the uni and ikura spoon, Wagyu, and the lightly torched salmon nigiri. The flavors were clean, balanced, and melt-in-your-mouth good. We also had the yuzu tea and sakura drink which paired really nicely with the meal. The omakase pacing was good! Just enough time to enjoy each piece without feeling rushed.\n\nThe restaurant itself has a cozy, intimate sushi bar vibe and the service was attentive throughout the meal. It's a great spot in Japantown for a date night or special occasion if you're craving high-quality sushi in the city.\n\nTotal for two came out to about $370 with two omakases ($98 each), supplements ($35 each), drinks ($6.50 per tea), tax, and tip. Worth it to add the $35 supplement of the O-Toro w/ caviar, uni ikura spoon, A5 wagyu. worth it for the experience. Would happily come back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tina Nguyen", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114113563226619364111/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtbyIf_v88hlCMKDrA2FtSHij2XWprEb6sMMpqeyrALw2g2MwL=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-08T07:20:59.476894862Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oR2FFVjFVWFo0ZWxGaGRIbFBiWHB3VURaMloyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oR2FFVjFVWFo0ZWxGaGRIbFBiWHB3VURaMloyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858145f40b31e1:0x283a08661e21a5ce"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOb1NGb3RNMWRrTjNwQmJreGhObFk0UlU1TlIyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "December 2025 Japanese restaurant specializing in Omakase style cuisine.  What makes them different is their mystery box style sushi 🍣 collection which is much of an IG feast in itself.\n\nService is standard and very informative\n\nThe place is very clean and bright with a relaxed layout with good privacy spacing.\n\nIdeal for small groups and casual dinning.\n\nNo in place toilet", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "December 2025 Japanese restaurant specializing in Omakase style cuisine.  What makes them different is their mystery box style sushi 🍣 collection which is much of an IG feast in itself.\n\nService is standard and very informative\n\nThe place is very clean and bright with a relaxed layout with good privacy spacing.\n\nIdeal for small groups and casual dinning.\n\nNo in place toilet", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "OcP_Fact finder_Info Sharer", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105836579422577440870/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXj27PLHJ_QSUhm-8w3zHHigffo5zncacWbSlAZAap6qwJPkk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-07T20:11:50.623700444Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOb1NGb3RNMWRrTjNwQmJreGhObFk0UlU1TlIyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOb1NGb3RNMWRrTjNwQmJreGhObFk0UlU1TlIyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858145f40b31e1:0x283a08661e21a5ce"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ4TEL9EWBhYARzqUhHmYIOig/photos/AWCwydiVH3mEn7IZN9-44Fpf0te9m9SntyKpW2wwEK3YDuHFwxJUVhPn-AOdX3rRHzTcMFGAg8_2c-nYL_LFdMeYm48MHG8v7QziOO6SgLqS0tNlyEGTX-W_UztVt4GJkby92SQ4L-zNNzCiZB7rqxAnFpo1Cz4d5GrQD17H74TegAQNiD5bRw3oy6tbX_774c5s0xpqtqyIvrOEW8sc0yYuJK_psW9USvtqSHt5SmgvZ94uzxVaFVzhE-K0Tqm5TQfYfyqJkGOaLBWgpRauWcJcqk3tXmv6cx-g0sSyxy8rQqWhHefmYWv5y2fAK9Z5ei13HVFdGahU1w1XLwlenBBUWipvejqnyUe_LHF9JKD1gOW4gG_6Qow7fxB-lo4P2eJJ0m99PRa0vt521uUSyzMP2n